Comment: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear viewers, feast your eyes on this ultimate super-lightweight machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This state-of-the-art aerofoil, able to convert even a crosswind into a forward thrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This saddle of pure molded carbon-fiber with no synthetic leather.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This pursuit of function and form that has merged into a single work of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes without saying that obtaining such a machine required much sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.52,0:00:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignoring my studies, laboring at part-time jobs,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sparing not a second for anything other than this bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I risked everything to obtain this machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.55,0:00:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this weekend is the Shimanami Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My victory there is almost guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at the end of my winning run,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finally be greeted by rose-colored campus life!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, can you bring it up? It's open...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am prepared for any contingency.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This lock is unbreakable, save against a hydraulic cutter...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.05,0:00:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's my bicycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take my two years away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.87,0:00:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just like that, the crystallization of my past two years goes down the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are called the Cheery Cycle Cleanup Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious autonomous circle that regulates illegal bicycle parking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first they were a group staffed by volunteers,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.51,0:01:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,diligently giving their time to maintain the campus,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in recent years they've taken on a strange look,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,forcibly removing any bicycles just a tad outside the designated area,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for them never to be seen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rumors are that they end up at bicycle rental shops around Kyoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or are transported across the Sea of Japan and sold to that country to the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, they've expanded their control to all of Kyoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so one cannot let down one's guard even when venturing off-campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:28.19,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H52368F&\bord1\fs40\fnChinacat_PL\move(776,119,749,96,0,5491)}Watch out for this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:28.19,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord1\fs40\fnChinacat_PL\c&H7E7570&\move(202,87,152,61,0,5450)}Never forgive the\NCycle Cleanup Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.75,0:01:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the hated enemy of all Kyoto college students,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a threat to our peaceful daily lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why has this happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must question the one responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is responsible for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a brand-spanking new freshman university student,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and before my eyes were innumerable open doors to rose-colored campus life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, once I found out I'd passed the entrance exam,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my heart had already been set on the allure of a single circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that circle's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:17.51,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\bord0\c&HBF4F9A&\frx25\fry0\blur2\pos(640,20)\fnBloklettersViltstiftFxd}Cycling Club Soleil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:17.55,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\bord0\c&HBF4F9A&\frx25\fry0\blur2\pos(640,20)\fnBloklettersViltstiftFxd}Cycling Club Soleil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:17.59,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\bord0\c&HBF4F9A&\frx25\fry0\blur2\pos(640,20)\fnBloklettersViltstiftFxd}Cycling Club Soleil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:17.63,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\bord0\c&HBF4F9A&\frx15\fry0\blur2\fs70\pos(640,40)\fnBloklettersViltstiftFxd}Cycling Club Soleil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:22.55,signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\c&HBF4F9A&\blur1\fs50\fad(0,1000)\fnBloklettersViltstiftFxd}Cycling Club Soleil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There lay my future of pure, sparking gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,together with raven-haired maidens in a fierce contest of the rendezvous of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the situation called for it, I'd even let them ride with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what I, an idiot beyond all redemption, had thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Icarus's wings, which were made of hardened wax,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,melted after he single-mindedly flew straight towards the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I, in pursuit of a rose-colored\Ncampus life, was indeed no different,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the Cycling Club was a club in name only;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it was more like a hardcore cycling team.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was quickly cast into despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and before my feet was a creature with a face like a fish-man risen from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend! Sink back into the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say some pretty cruel things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am your compatriot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my first contact with Ozu, as well as my worst contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what they find fun about rotating their legs so fast they wear away the cartilage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do something more fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go on a run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you resist, there's no escaping your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Training was as harsh as you could imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with the belief that I would overcome the suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and reach my rose-colored future, I continued to turn the pedals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the world of "roadies", only the fast are recognized and praised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speed is king! Speed is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In high school, I didn't belong to any sports clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I did as few activities as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and just stayed cooped up with a bunch of other layabout guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So a full-blown athletic team was far too great a burden for me to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I attempted to train,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with my feeble constitution, there was no certainty of improvement,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and of course there was no way I'd place well in any competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I shuffled along, wasting my freshman year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, you're just eating chicken like a damn fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, this is the best source of protein!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my... It must be a struggle for a poor fellow like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of chicken, how about letting me eat some salted tongue with green onions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you eat some of this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ozu never showed his face in the circle,\Nbut he'd frequently show up in my room.
